        },
        {
          "quote": "- Night-side constraints are weaker than day-side constraints in the current dataset.",
          "line_ref": "L50"
        },
        {
          "quote": "5. Remaining degeneracies motivate broader wavelength coverage and repeated observations.",
          "line_ref": "L44"
        }
      ],
      "caveat": "Because multiple atmospheric scenarios (including O2-rich cases) are not fully ruled out and modeling degeneracies remain significant, conclusions about specific compositions should be treated as provisional."
    }
  ]
